      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered and garage-kept its whole life, and it drives like a dream. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
