    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This specimen boasts a comprehensive mechanical pedigree: the VANOS system has been fully overhauled, rod bearings replaced with treated shells, and the rear subframe proactively reinforced with plates. The naturally aspirated inline-six breathes through individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power to a factory mechanical limited-slip differential. Chassis dynamics are preserved via fresh OEM bushings and a meticulous alignment. This is a turn-key, concours-level example for the collector who demands mechanical perfection and structural integrity.",
