    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since its original purchase. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with a professional ceramic coating; there are absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings to be found. The wheels are free of any curb rash and are wrapped in premium tires with near-full tread depth. Inside, the cabin remains in an 'as-new' state\u2014the premium leather upholstery shows no creasing or bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and the original protective films are still present on several interior trim pieces. Mechanically, the car is flawless. It features a full, documented service history exclusively through authorized dealerships, with the most recent major service and fluid flush completed just 200 miles ago. All systems, from the adaptive suspension to the advanced infotainment suite, operate perfectly. This is a one-owner, non-smoker vehicle with zero accidents and a clean title. If you are looking for a collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor, this is the one.",
